name: Custom Image classifier 250x250 Object Detector

input_tensor_metadata.description: Input image to be classified. The expected image is 250 x 250, with three channels (red, blue, and green) per pixel. Each value in the tensor is a single byte between 0 and 255.

associated_files.description: Labels for objects that the model can recognize.
